timing_report_...t_timing_slack(25.10)  timing_report_...t_timing_slack(25.10)

Name
       timing_report_drv_use_worst_timing_slack

Syntax
       timing_report_drv_use_worst_timing_slack

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       Enables  reporting of the worst DRV slack across all the views for con-
       figurable DRV report.

       When set to true, the software shows a non-default special case report,
       where timing slacks for MMMC flow is the worst among all active views.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

